Chart Retuner — third-party notices
===================================

Since v0.5.0 this plugin ships no vendored third-party
components: the runtime is plain ES modules under src/, and rendering is
done by the feedBack host's own highway.

Historical note: versions before 0.5.0 shipped their own copy of the
bundled highway_3d
renderer and vendored Butterchurn / butterchurn-presets (MIT, Copyright
(c) Jordan Berg and the MilkDrop preset community) under assets/vendor/
for the 'butterchurn' background style, and loaded Three.js (MIT) from
feedBack core's vendored copy. All of that was removed in v0.5.0.
